The '''3rd Legion Tercio "Don Juan de Austria"''' is a regiment of the [[Spanish Legion]]. Its headquarters are in [[Viator]]. The 3rd Tercio contains the VII Legion Bandera "Valenzuela"  and VIII Spanish Legion Bandera "[[Christopher Columbus|Colón]]".

