{{unreferenced|date=April 2018}}
'''August & Telma''' are a pop duo from [[Iceland]]. They comprise members Einar Ágúst Víðisson and Telma Ágústsdóttir and are best known for representing Iceland in the [[Eurovision Song Contest 2000]] with the song "[[Tell Me!]]". The song was an upbeat one, varying from [[pop music|pop]] to [[soft rock]]. The song placed 12th from 24 participating songs with 45 points. 

