{{Infobox Airline |airline = Nouvelle Air Affaires Gabon |logo = |logo_size = |fleet_size = 4 |destinations = |IATA = – |ICAO = NVS |callsign = NOUVELLE AFFAIRES |parent = |company_slogan = |founded = 1975 |headquarters = [[Libreville]], [[Gabon]] |key_people = |hubs = [[Libreville International Airport]] |secondary_hubs = |focus_cities = |frequent_flyer = |lounge = |alliance = }}
'''Nouvelle Air Affaires Gabon''' is an [[airline]] based in [[Libreville]], [[Gabon]]. It operates corporate and freight charter services. Its main base is [[Libreville International Airport]].<ref name="FI">{{Cite news| title= Directory: World Airlines | work= [[Flight International]] | page= 57 | date= 2007-04-10}}</ref> It started operating out of Gabon in 1975.{{Citation needed|date=June 2007}}
Following the closure of [[Afrijet]] and [[Gabon Airlines]], Nouvelle Air Affaires Gabon is the last carrier in Gabon not on the [[list of air carriers banned in the European Union]].
